name: Bird at Tent Rocks
description: This is an archival pigment ink print on 100%, bright white cotton rag matte photo paper. The print is hand-numbered and signed on the front. It comes in a clear plastic archival bag with backing, colorfully taped inside the mailer. Each print is made by hand and may differ from the colors you see on your monitor. Included with each order is a free 2.5" x 2.5" mini print from one of the photos in my Instagram feed. The package is ready to receive as a gift and is sprinkled with a little Santa Fe magic. Please email me via the Contact page with any questions.
